snippet.title: Amber Heard looks emotionally drained as she hugs companion - Daily Mail
snippet.description:
It seems her nasty divorce from Johnny Depp is taking it's toll. Amber Heard was spotted on Saturday heading to an LA-area church, and then later leaving after apparently having become emotional. The 30-year-old beauty was dressed down for the outing, as she no doubt wanted to keep her visit as low profile as possible.
